	<phrase id="21" desc="">
		<original>
			Remember that there were many others who died by crucifixion in the first century. It was not that Jesus was physically crucified that makes Him unique; it was that He was crucified for you, in your place. He died on the cross for you.
		</original>
		<translated>
			De nombreuses personnes sont mortes par crucifixion au 1 siècle. La crucifixion de Jésus est unique dans l'histoire de l'humanité, non par sa cruauté, mais parce qu’il est mort volontairement à notre place. Jésus est mort pour toi.
		</translated>
	</phrase>

